Zhou Ju's current address is

20
00:01:29,570 --> 00:01:30,769
No. 42,

21
00:01:30,770 --> 00:01:32,150
Lane 5,

22
00:01:32,610 --> 00:01:34,400
Yanghua Road.

23
00:01:39,130 --> 00:01:40,240
