59
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:42,400
(I've been trying to keep myself posted on you)
(I'm aware the police are after me.)

60
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:44,480
(So it's time for me to explain myself.)

61
00:04:46,570 --> 00:04:48,950
(During the Yingqiao project,)

62
