64
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:56,480
(I ever expressed my objection)

65
00:04:56,650 --> 00:04:58,419
(as the person in charge
of the project.)

66
00:04:58,420 --> 00:04:59,920
(And I thought of quitting.)

67
00:05:01,090 --> 00:05:03,259
(Yet in the face
of the tempting, enormous profit,)

68
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:04,990
(I couldn't say no to it)

69
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:07,040
