(After that,)

72
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:14,329
(during the inspection
of the department involved,)

73
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:16,040
(the beans were spilled.)

74
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:18,379
(Mo Sanxing then made me)

75
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:19,990
(take all the blame.)

76
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:22,870
(He tried to send me abroad,)

77
00:05:22,940 --> 00:05:25,280
(making me look like a fugitive.)

78
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:28,950
(I've been in hiding)

79
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:31,160
(for the past three years.)

80
00:05:31,770 --> 00:05:34,630
(It's actually because I haven't been
able to tell you this.)

81
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:37,720
(I've been trying to keep myself posted on you)
(Xiling. Come with me.)

82
00:05:39,130 --> 00:05:40,830
(I'm more aware than ever)

83
00:05:41,090 --> 00:05:43,040
(that I made that decision)

84
00:05:43,060 --> 00:05:44,280
(for money.)

85
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:49,800
(I thought you'd give up on seeking
the truth after these three years.)

86
00:05:50,450 --> 00:05:53,360
(That's why I've been in hiding
without much thought.)

87
00:05:54,330 --> 00:05:57,800
(Little did I expect
that you'd never give up on it.)

88
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:04,990
This is the outcome of the meeting.
Gu Zhaohe is elected chairman.

89
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:12,720
(Xiling.)

90
00:06:13,090 --> 00:06:15,310
(Please forgive me for being avoidant
all these years.)

91
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:19,040
(In fact, I've had a copy
of Yingqiao's genuine invoices)

92
00:06:19,210 --> 00:06:21,560
(and the relevant data from back then.)

93
00:06:22,300 --> 00:06:23,830
(In order to avoid getting found out,)

94
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:26,480
(I hid it in my photo with you.)

95
00:06:27,010 --> 00:06:28,280
(All this is more than enough)

96
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:31,070
(to serve as the evidence used
to testify against Mo Sanxing.)

97
00:07:52,010 --> 00:07:53,390
Xiling.

98
00:07:57,580 --> 00:08:03,520
♪It only takes a few romantic gestures
for one to feel touched♪

99
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:10,760
♪Because with a heart full of love,
everything is delightful♪

100
00:08:12,260 --> 00:08:18,200
♪Loneliness fades away in our hugs♪

101
