111
00:08:55,050 --> 00:08:56,160
Xiling.

112
00:08:57,010 --> 00:08:59,070
I have something to say to you.

113
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:01,280
What's it?

114
00:09:02,010 --> 00:09:03,099
I still remember

115
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:04,880
I first came here

116
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:06,680
to approach you.

117
00:09:07,170 --> 00:09:09,280
However, little did I know

118
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:12,000
