to do something about it.

127
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:54,800
I want to end
our current relationship here,

128
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:57,920
where we first met each other.

129
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:11,310
I never expected

130
00:10:12,770 --> 00:10:14,950
